# Recommendation Marker

- Whenever you recommend an option, choice, or course of action, mark it with a star emoji (⭐) so it stands out visually.
- Put the ⭐ at the start of the recommended item, e.g. `⭐ Use Postgres` or label it `(⭐ Recommended)`.
- Only the recommended option gets the star — never star the non-recommended alternatives.
- When presenting multiple options, still mark exactly one as the ⭐ recommendation unless you genuinely have no preference.
